Guard every form against direct access
Add this to Form_Load of every form (frmLogShipment, frmStudies, frmShipments, frmSettings, frmAdmin) as the very first lines:
vb

If gCurrentTechID = 0 Then
    MsgBox "You are not authorised to access this form.", vbCritical, "Access Denied"
    DoCmd.Close acForm, Me.Name
    Exit Sub
End If
